The original map that I have edited was made by S.Branck, and credit goes to him for making it.

I have simply made an underground bit for anti-camper, hence the name. I have also changed a few textures and included a few extra parts to the map. -No crouching glitching in the middle part now.

Took me about 3 days to edit and change things around.

Enjoy :D
